  ('medical-tech-moex-20155', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-b92db706', 'sub-medical-tech-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '測定精液中果糖時，加入硫酸鋅靜置室溫15分鐘後離心的步驟是為達成以下何種目的？ 去除精蟲  去除蛋白  保存果糖  保存磷酸', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "964fc8399abe", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20156', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-b92db706', 'sub-medical-tech-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '試紙法及磺基水楊酸法測定尿蛋白之比較，以下何者正確？ 皆可測得白蛋白及球蛋白   皆以顏色改變來判讀 皆受高度鹼性尿干擾    皆受大量維生素C干擾', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "964fc8399abe", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20157', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-b92db706', 'sub-medical-tech-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列驗尿試紙條所含成分何者正確？ 測尿蛋白及比重皆含酸鹼指示劑  測葡萄糖及白血球酯 皆含酵素 測潛血及膽紅素皆含重氮鹽  測尿膽素原及亞硝酸鹽含Ehrlich’s試劑', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "964fc8399abe", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
